<%= form_for @user do |f| %>
Name <%= f.text_field :name %><br><br>

Height (in inches)
<%= f.number_field :height %><br><br>

How happy are you? (1-5 scale)
<%= f.number_field :happiness %><br><br>

How nauseous are you? (1-5 scale)
<%= f.number_field :nausea %><br><br>

How many dollars are in your pocket?
<%= f.number_field :tickets %><br><br>

Check box if you are a theme park owner <%= f.check_box :admin %><br><br>

Password <%= f.password_field :password %><br><br>

<%= f.submit %>

<% end %>
